{"tid":876881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安倍訪華點滴：驚現草間彌生山寨展","createTime":"2018-10-26T02:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T05:56:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"09c7126e3ad7f10214ab730a3af95e40df4205f6","tid":876881,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T02:42:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181026/20531117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181026%2F20531117&d=JNhKgI4EBlNO5oCOrzAP5v1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=06947317\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181026%2F20531117&h=57db4fcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181026/20531117</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018年10月26日 <br />\n<br />\n安倍訪華點滴：驚現草間彌生山寨展<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181026/large/26cf05p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181026%2Flarge%2F26cf05p.jpg&h=511489d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中日文化交流迅速回暖，但中國卻出現日著名藝術家草間彌生和村上隆的山寨展覽（圖）。日本經濟新聞網指，一個名為「草間彌生&times;村上隆藝術雙聯展」自今年4月以來，至少在深圳、廣州、武漢、上海四地舉辦。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，展覽上大量展出冒充「波點女王」草間作品的繪畫和雕塑等，但草間和村上均未參與創作這些作品，作品被認為係贗品。展覽在購物中心舉辦時免費對公眾開放，但在上海的展覽卻收取60元人民幣（下同，約67港元）的單人票或100元（約113港元）的親子票。<br />\n<br />\n草間和村上二人均指「此舉侵犯了自身的著作權，並違反中國法律」，正研究從刑事和民事對策展公司展開法律行動。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n安倍訪華點滴：晚宴嘆松茸湯粉蒸肉<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n習結束南巡　評論員轟徒具形式<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n39年涉款2,547億　日終止援華<br />\n<br />\n中共恐日加入反華「毒丸計劃」<br />\n<br />\n安倍訪華點滴：晚宴嘆松茸湯粉蒸肉<br />\n<br />\n京奉承安倍　離間美日習今峯會恭迎　勢掀高潮"},{"pid":"d5e780668b0b924069f6642a8c0368f4126e0bcc","tid":876881,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T03:21:17.000Z","msg":"amazing chi na"},{"pid":"cbc348a845ca803ac563defe47d98912f475ae9a","tid":876881,"uid":17534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T05:37:02.000Z","msg":"完全無辦法理解到點解可以咁樣做<br />\n你以人地名義開展覽"},{"pid":"f04fe2abdf1a832efad6ee163efc5bc63e9777f7","tid":876881,"uid":17534,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cbc348a845ca803ac563defe47d98912f475ae9a","tid":876881,"uid":17534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T05:37:02.000Z","msg":"完全無辦法理解到點解可以咁樣做<br />\n你以人地名義開展覽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T05:40:34.000Z","msg":"人地都89 歲 最尾個幾年先嚟啲咁既野刺激佢<br />\n如果佢地認識草間彌生 有讀過佢既background <br />\n就應該知道佢係當呢啲作品係佢既全部 <br />\n令自己唔自殺既精神支柱<br />\n<br />\n但我地偉大既祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係理解唔到為咗賺錢可以去到咁盡"},{"pid":"cc2d83ea0d8dbcfca0b4fc88279a77110a293dce","tid":876881,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T05:42:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>草間和村上二人均指「此舉侵犯了自身的著作權，並違反中國法律」，正研究從刑事和民事對策展公司展開法律行動</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n告返你轉頭呀柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1df92849bb8ede6530f997ad60b0c9a03ae5786","tid":876881,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc2d83ea0d8dbcfca0b4fc88279a77110a293dce","tid":876881,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T05:42:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>草間和村上二人均指「此舉侵犯了自身的著作權，並違反中國法律」，正研究從刑事和民事對策展公司展開法律行動</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n告返你轉頭呀柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T05:49:27.000Z","ms